# API Runtime Role Rules

- Read `docs/ai/services/api.md` before structural changes.
- If the repository family is `backend-service`, read the backend-service family rule together with this rule.
- Preserve controller, service, model/VO, repository, and query repository boundaries.
- Check config, security, API contract, DB compatibility, and rollout impact together.
- If schema or query work is involved, also read `docs/ai/database-rules.md`.
- Prefer compile or test verification before completion.
